{"tid":1884964,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[內附騙徙資料庫] 到底有幾弱智先會入錢買口罩？","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T03:46:33.000Z","uid":182994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75c92e2be4f8be390ddbbdacd4c9d2872dd2af2f","tid":1884964,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"平少少一盒就即刻入錢狗衝<br />\n班人本身係為左搵錢，如果佢真係短期內有現貨，貴一貴都唔憂冇人要，點會平賣比你<br />\n<br />\n自己去口罩集中個post睇下，普通人有幾難訂大量歐美日韓口罩，你唔係覺得Carousell 或者 facebook個mk仔mk妹可以訂到大量貨下嘛？<br />\n<br />\n附上騙徒口罩資料庫tg channel  入去睇下自己有冇中伏<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/findmasks_faker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindmasks_faker&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=2cd6ad8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/findmasks_faker</a>"},{"pid":"3de745f84453b4cc32da25d273ba969ece33b289","tid":1884964,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"比柒婆搞到無曬理智"},{"pid":"5bd8192fa449f807d923cc0d1a12070daa3bd0eb","tid":1884964,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"#防騙教學 <br />\n匯豐早前喺facebook曾經出過提防網購受騙嘅教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1102154686517549/posts/2730339980365670/?substory_index=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1102154686517549%2Fposts%2F2730339980365670%2F%3Fsubstory_index%3D0&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=778d6e56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1102154686517549/posts/2730339980365670/?substory_index=0</a><br />\n雖然出post嘅匯豐係做過令港人討厭嘅嘢<br />\n但入面提到嘅內容，的確有助大家防止進行網購期間受騙<br />\n值得參考一下<br />\n<br />\n匯豐提供防止受騙嘅方法：<br />\n//<br />\n💡購買時應了解賣家嘅背景、過往記錄、聲譽同其他買家嘅評價<br />\n💡留意價錢有無過於「超值」<br />\n💡注意唔尋常嘅收貨日期，例如要一個月後開始送貨<br />\n💡小心有唔合理及無退款保障嘅交易<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得有咁大隻夾乸隨街跳啦，唔洗排，唔洗上網登記，唔洗捕amazon，唔洗比人cut單，仲要有人用成本價賣比你，諗下有冇可能"},{"pid":"bb960153a407f7c1fffb982861a7dd59c47a7ab3","tid":1884964,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de745f84453b4cc32da25d273ba969ece33b289","tid":1884964,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"比柒婆搞到無曬理智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"個同事話比人呃錢 講足成個星期<br />\n心諗你咁都信 唔呃你呃邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98fd4f5fc30fca3c20899e62ab661205743ce16","tid":1884964,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"香港人真係能柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b672249749cd45b9ecb614cc67f53e3375b93590","tid":1884964,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/18/112711_6d7217831a606d0c6a4e71e8bf663dcd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2F112711_6d7217831a606d0c6a4e71e8bf663dcd.jpeg&h=23d1638b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己睇下美國一盒賣緊幾錢，話呢排開團果啲都好信？"},{"pid":"c8b43e3ee994a2e87def5eeeb4773803af37aa94","tid":1884964,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb13a39c0b03301d3e9a49cc5ff76f4aed6b97e2","tid":1884964,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:28:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a75c5e20c4ee477b41dec1f3e5cd733e02f5065b","tid":1884964,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a3ba26c3328fd89c174cbc815c923af80a6ac8a","tid":1884964,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"但係個騙徒用銀行戶口...<br />\n銀行一check就知你邊個啦<br />\n兩邊係到鬥弱智？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f359f77aaceaa7824394b13cebb9a7b20c8f08e","tid":1884964,"